Package de.feu.massim22.group3.agents

Class BdiAgentV1

java.lang.Object
de.feu.massim22.group3.agents.Agent
de.feu.massim22.group3.agents.BdiAgent<IDesire>
de.feu.massim22.group3.agents.BdiAgentV1
All Implemented Interfaces:
Supervisable, Runnable
public class BdiAgentV1 extends BdiAgent<IDesire> implements Runnable, Supervisable
The class BdiAgentV1 defines an agent implementation of group 3 in the massim agent contest 2022. The class is one variant out of two implementations of the group. The other implementation is BdiAgentV2. Please be aware, that BdiAgentV1 is no predecessor of BdiAgentV2. Both implementations define a separate approach and are not connected to each other.
Author:
Heinz Stadler
